name: Cindy Xinmin Chen
content: Cindy Chen's Home Page Cindy Chen, Ph.D. Head & Associate Professor Richard Miner School Computer and Information Sciences Dandeneau 316A University of Massachussetts Lowell One University Avenue Lowell, MA 01854 Email: cchen AT cs.uml.edu Teaching Research Service Born in Xi'an, China. Received B.S. degree in Space Physics from Peking University, China, M.S. and Ph.D. degrees in Computer Science from University of California, Los Angeles. Research interests include Spatio-Temporal Databases, Data Mining, Cloud Computing and Big Data, etc.
